================================================================================
RECOMMENDATIONS:
================================================================================
• FP16 (Half Precision): Best choice for deployment - 2x memory savings, faster
• FP32 (Full Precision): Use only if FP16 causes numerical instability

NOTE: Moondream's custom architecture is not compatible with bitsandbytes
quantization. For aggressive quantization, consider:
  1. Model pruning techniques
  2. Knowledge distillation to a smaller model
  3. ONNX Runtime with quantization

